Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.07,0:00:03.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}在风的节奏中推理变得清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}与黑色的关联也能看得清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}总觉得有点奇怪啊 黑衣男子们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}在这次事件中一定要把他们逮住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k218}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.79,0:00:15.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:30.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}海风中感觉到你的气息 银色的波浪消除了我们两人的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.74,0:00:43.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就这样让时间停止的话 可以看到远处小小的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.25,0:00:53.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经无法分离 决定就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在闪耀的季节里终于到达的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.14,0:01:08.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要再迷惘 相信我的眼眸 风的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.27,0:01:15.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即将漫溢的不安 隐藏了眼泪的昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.99,0:01:25.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}遥远的回忆现在终于可以说出 风的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.75,0:01:44.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}打扰一下 毛利侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}在这次的杀人事件里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}被逮捕的南云先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}据说是无法忍受伸晴先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}受到风见先生的暴力对待才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他这样说的话就是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我仅仅是揭穿了他使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.40,0:02:06.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}并劝他在证据被说出来之前去自首而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.25,0:02:12.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}毛利先生 请等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.89,0:02:18.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}男人以背影取胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我帅呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.76,0:02:28.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}难得一次在清醒状态下解决了事件 就得意成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让叔叔成为名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.22,0:02:35.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}是为了得到黑衣男子们的情报 而不得不这样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么一点都没有消息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.04,0:02:39.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}倒回去 倒回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}那些家伙通过暗杀来筹集资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让灰原他们做出奇怪的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.11,0:02:50.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}并且召集很多优秀的电脑程序设计师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底 到底是想干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你好 这里是毛利侦探事务所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}该不会是那些人花钱想开发电脑游戏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.05,0:03:08.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}游戏的系统工程师失踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}希望我们找到那个人对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}喂 找我的话就说我不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}马上就是洋子演的电视剧的重播了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}我一定要录下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}是 现在的话也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}反正父亲今天没什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快把领带系好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.79,0:03:40.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}游戏的系统工程师失踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:55.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}遗留的无声证言（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.86,0:03:59.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个人就是一个星期前不知去向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.74,0:04:02.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}系统工程师板仓吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.57,0:04:08.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说他这次失踪不是第一次的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那家伙在受委托开发的游戏期限快到了的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}经常会不见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k223}这次我觉得也是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.45,0:04:22.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}但是我们不能老是吮着手指等他出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.80,0:04:26.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}上次报警后那家伙大发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以这次想拜托你来找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像和那些家伙没关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以如果知道了他在哪里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}请务必和我联系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.59,0:04:39.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}喂 有没有搞错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}我们才是最急的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k254}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.44,0:04:46.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k103}这次最先委托他开发系统的可是我们公司啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:51.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个 你们不是一个公司的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:56.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是委托板仓先生开发围棋系统的须贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.83,0:05:00.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我叫內藤 是委托他开发国际象棋系统的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我委托的是将棋系统 我叫相马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是一个人能在同时开发三种游戏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以我们要找到他 问他是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}原来说好不是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}在我们分别和他谈这件事的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.38,0:05:19.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}那家伙分别和我们这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}“现在我和哪里都没有签约 就交给我吧”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那你们是什么时候知道他还兼职其他工作的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.25,0:05:30.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一星期前他给我们三个人发了这封邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一下子做三个游戏还真累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这段时间心脏也不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k239}所以离开事务所一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}好好放松 从昨天开始…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}是这个人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k169}照片上戴着眼镜 没有认出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这不是因为做CG而很有名的板仓卓先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.52,0:05:55.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 他在公共场合是戴隐形眼镜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你认识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.24,0:06:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k145}是啊 在电影的职员表上经常看到他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}三年前因为眼睛不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}所以退出了CG的开发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}开始专注于开发系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k279}那么有名的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}会不会是被绑架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:14.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k121}不 如果是那个男人的话说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.75,0:06:23.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概两年前在板仓的事务所碰到过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}长着浓密的胡子 一口关西腔的大个子男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}內藤你也一定看到过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.63,0:06:35.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}在今年满天堂的新作发布会上他也来了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}龙舌兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个大个子男人说了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}在事务所里到底说了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k294}不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.15,0:06:51.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k182}我到的时候就听到他说“你已经没有用了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}只有这些 应该还有什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}喂 柯南 你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.60,0:06:58.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.84,0:07:03.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}看来只有找到板仓 直接问他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个男人应该已经在那次爆炸里死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有关系了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.67,0:07:13.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}问题是怎样从这个画面里把他找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是哪里的宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}宾馆的话因为事关顾客的隐私 是不会告诉我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}反正他也是用假名入住的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.09,0:07:26.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.62,0:07:31.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k153}我今天晚上想吃生鱼片 天津饭和炖牛肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.08,0:07:35.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等 这不是日式料理 中华料理和西餐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一家店里不可能吃得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}那么如果一个人同时定了这三种料理的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}就会被认为是奇怪的客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}奇怪的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确这家伙的房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}同时有围棋 国际象棋和将棋的棋盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有没有问他从事务所带走了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他惯用的笔记本电脑和几张装有数据的光盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他把这些装到包里就出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}除了这些什么都没带吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.36,0:08:05.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请问是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.21,0:08:15.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}我就是同时借了围棋 将棋和国际象棋的那位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}房间的电话突然打不通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}现在用手机在打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}快帮我想点办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.26,0:08:25.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}不好意思 我们这里没有准备这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 对不起 打错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯 接下去是新米花宾馆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}同时借了围棋 将棋和国际象棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}并且在宾馆住了一个星期以上的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该会在宾馆的服务员之间引起话题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在在用手机打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}能不能快点帮我想点办法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k135}啊 是2004室的板仓先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是是…2004室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}我们马上转告相关部门的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 只不过是电话插头掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.13,0:09:07.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}新米花宾馆2004室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.85,0:09:12.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的 为什么你们也要跟来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就会找麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.81,0:09:15.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}可是 是柯南…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}叔叔你好狡猾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k166}你是想完事后一个人吃宾馆好吃的料理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好啦 没关系啦 侦探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}如果找到板仓先生的话我们请客好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这里就是他的藏身之处吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是你们不是商业竞争对手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么会一起到我这里来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.16,0:09:50.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为我们从那封邮件知道他同时在做三个游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}三个负责人想碰个头谈一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后我就想委托毛利先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个不是我提出来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}委托侦探的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}但是提出毛利先生名字的可是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.93,0:10:08.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}笨蛋 打电话的可是我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.73,0:10:14.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}啊 洋子的电视剧已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}戴那么便宜的表会被他说的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.46,0:10:23.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}板仓对于手表很挑剔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}所以 看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.22,0:10:25.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k125}看吧 我们也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k111}你们戴的是真品吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}笨蛋 这可是我五天前才买的新品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}你戴的才是假货吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.82,0:10:43.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好意思 内藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}麻烦你按一下20楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:46.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k122}嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}板仓先生看到我们大家都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.03,0:10:57.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}一定会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.58,0:11:03.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是我们这样直接去房间没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}板仓可是和组织一员龙舌兰有关系的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兰和叔叔 以及这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}就这么拥过去真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:21.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}龙舌兰跟板仓说的是“你已经没有用了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:25.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说没有利用价值了 可能会被杀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果说为了除掉板仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}那些家伙也潜伏在附近的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.66,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}不 说不定已经等在房间里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.27,0:11:39.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}笨蛋 我在瞎着急些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k227}冷静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}龙舌兰跟板仓说那句话是在两年之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k275}如果他们有这个打算的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}板仓现在就已经被杀掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且板仓如果是组织的一员的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.33,0:11:57.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不应该会在跟龙舌兰碰面的时候接见相马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}总之 等碰到板仓之后一定要好好的问他一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:10.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}龙舌兰到底是出于什么目的拜访板仓的事务所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪啊 明明挂着“请勿打扰”的牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概出去吃饭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k237}那我们在房间外面等一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好意思 麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为是自动锁 所以一定要记得带钥匙出门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.00,0:12:39.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.79,0:12:43.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}服务员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}能不能帮我把叔叔的房间也打开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.82,0:12:53.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他忘了我们要回来 自己出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k106}快一点 我憋不住啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要尿了 要尿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.74,0:13:04.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k247}真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}干得不错啊 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}因为如果板仓先生回来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k262}看到门口那么多人 也许会逃掉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是小弟弟 好像没这个必要了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}板仓先生就在那里打瞌睡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.91,0:13:26.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 起来 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}你已经逃不掉了 板仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}板仓 板仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.92,0:13:53.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.32,0:13:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}已经死了超过一天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}我去报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}为什么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.06,0:14:07.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}恐怕是心脏病突发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}桌子上散落着药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}心脏病突然发作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}想吃药的时候已经来不及 就这么去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k99}都是因为你一个人躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}板仓不是因为疾病而自然死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是被谁谋杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k211}但是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}为什么只差一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那些家伙的线索又断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.89,0:14:44.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.87,0:14:46.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}日记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}板仓先生的日记吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.67,0:14:55.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}如果是的话 也许可以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}龙舌兰来见板仓先生的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}黑衣组织的那些家伙到底想干些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看了这个也许…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k215}会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要乱碰死者的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.69,0:15:18.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的 一放松就乱碰东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可恶 还是拿不到嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看来要看日记内容的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}就一定要让叔叔知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.22,0:15:31.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k273}板仓不是心脏病自然死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而是死于他杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.72,0:15:39.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 犯人很有可能就在这三个人里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死者叫板仓卓 45岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是游戏的系统工程师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么死因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}虽然无法断言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}没有明显外伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}根据他服用过冠状动脉扩充剂的情况来判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该是死于突发性心脏病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恐怕死亡时间距今已有两天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警部 已经和板仓先生的主治医生联系上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}据说板仓先生的心脏病情况恶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.15,0:16:19.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}本来在这次的工作结束后就准备动手术的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.03,0:16:22.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}好像没有你出场的机会了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k274}啊 好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 死亡已经两天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}为什么宾馆的人没有注意到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.92,0:16:38.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为这个人在工作中是很讨厌被人打扰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.58,0:16:44.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}上次他书桌上的资料被移动了十厘米 就勃然大怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.43,0:16:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}反正他自己家里的床单也很少换的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可能拒绝了房间清扫服务吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}那三个人是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.46,0:16:58.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k235}是委托板仓开发系统的游戏公司的职员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:17:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他们委托我把一星期前失踪的板仓找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说 好不容易找到他的藏身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k269}却发现已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.97,0:17:11.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.00,0:17:17.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}明知道自己心脏不好 还一个人偷偷躲在宾馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}变成这样也不是不可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我觉得这个大叔很喜欢干净啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为我们进这个房间的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.47,0:17:31.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大叔坐在椅子上 把脸贴在桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是桌子上什么痕迹也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}口水的痕迹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}像他这样流口水的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.67,0:17:43.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}桌子上应该会沾到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k207}肯定是这个大叔擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k127}因为心脏病突发很痛苦的人 连药都拿不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}怎么可能擦掉留在桌子上的口水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k259}那么是谁擦掉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}而且我可是第一次听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}他原来是坐在椅子上 把头贴在桌子上的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我们推了一下就倒在地上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}如果是这样的话就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是尸体的手的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k226}如果死者是脸贴在桌子上死的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.19,0:18:20.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}尸体僵硬后 手应该保持夹在桌子和身体之间的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是哪里都看不到这样的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:27.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说板仓是死在其他地方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是啊 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.84,0:18:34.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}尸体的手和脚不是完全按照这个姿势僵硬的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}如果不是有人把板仓绑在椅子上的话就很难…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}可能板仓被绑在椅子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}并保持双手放在胸口的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.52,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k277}所以才吃不到本来要吃的药的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那 这该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是我们 也是你的强项
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}杀人事件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.91,0:19:13.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}但是这样的话 应该会有被绑过的痕迹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么样 法医
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}虽然没有很明显的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.99,0:19:24.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是有大范围的被外部压迫过的淤血的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}这条毯子好柔软 看上去真暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k126}不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}可是这是什么啊 到处黏乎乎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 是毛毯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}毛毯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.45,0:19:47.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}犯人恐怕是用毛毯把板仓的身体裹起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让他坐在椅子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}然后从上面用胶带绑了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.46,0:19:57.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后在腹部夹上枕头什么的 做成靠在椅子上的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}这样的话就没有绑过的痕迹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.38,0:20:07.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}这么说来 固定椅子的就是这张桌子的桌脚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.20,0:20:13.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然被擦过了 还留有一点胶带的黏着物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说 犯人把板仓就这样扔在房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.49,0:20:24.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后等板仓因为心脏病发作死亡 并且全身僵硬后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再回到这个房间 把胶带和毛毯处理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}伪装成是自然病死的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好 去问问宾馆的职员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.22,0:20:37.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}调查一下这两三天有没有可疑人物出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.46,0:20:37.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}宾馆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}说起来 那时为了调查板仓的藏身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}曾经冒充他给这个宾馆打过电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说我是同时借了围棋 将棋和国际象棋的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}房间的电话突然打不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}快帮我解决一下 什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后才知道了这个房间的号码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那时电话那头笑了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说“怎么又来了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.05,0:21:05.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.39,0:21:11.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}也就是说 可能有另外的人 和你用一样的手段调查咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.16,0:21:16.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 能够和我毛利小五郎拥有一样头脑的人物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警部 有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.34,0:21:22.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}有冒充板仓打电话来 说他房间电话不通的可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.83,0:21:24.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}随后职员到了板仓的房间时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}板仓说“不是我” 将他们赶了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.59,0:21:35.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}看上去犯人应该就是这个打电话的人没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是你怎么知道板仓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.03,0:21:42.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}向宾馆借了围棋 将棋还有国际象棋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.53,0:21:49.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}是看了板仓发给他们三个人的 有画面的邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.44,0:21:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看到了围棋 将棋和国际象棋的棋盘放在板仓面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k167}你们三个人都有可能用和毛利一样的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.02,0:22:06.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}查到这里 然后来过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.98,0:22:09.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.83,0:22:11.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k185}怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.36,0:22:35.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然我很坚强 但听到你在电话中的声音就会想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.30,0:22:42.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}尽管会受伤 但即使这样 还是想要和你相见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.71,0:22:48.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}总是这样背对着结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.59,0:22:55.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你为了给我回音很困难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.47,0:23:04.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}每次想到那个无法掩饰的表情
